startOviposition(uint256).details: Requests random numbers from Chainlink to determine number of eggs to lay and the dying chance

params._antId: ID of ant to lay eggs

returns.requestId: Request ID of random number request from Chainlink

updatePrices(uint256,uint256).details: Only the governor can call this

withdrawEther(address,uint256).details: Only the governor can call this

withdrawEtherBalance(address).details: Only the governor can call this

withdrawLink(address,uint256).details: Only the governor can call this

withdrawLinkBalance(address).details: Only the governor can call this

acceptOwnership().notice: Allows an ownership transfer to be completed by the recipient.

createAnt().notice: Creates an ant with an egg. Burns the egg and mints an ant to msg.sender

sellAnt(uint256).notice: Sell an ant for `s_antPrice`. Ant is squashed but can be reincarnated.

startOviposition(uint256).notice: Starts oviposition if oviposition period has been reached. Ant dying chance increases as eggs layed increases

transferOwnership(address).notice: Allows an owner to begin transferring ownership to a new address.

updatePrices(uint256,uint256).notice: Updates egg and ant price. Ant price must always be less than egg price
